style="display:inline-block;background:#1a4bb5;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 30px;border-radius:30px;font-weight:bold;">
Visit IIC Lakshya </a>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- FOOTER -->

<tr>
<td style="background:#0b2563;padding:25px;text-align:center;">

<div style="color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;">
IIC Lakshya
